y Residential Center, Karnes City, Texas.</p></li><li><a class="gallery-zoom" href="https://placesjournal.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Taylor-Border-Slideshow-TX-16.jpg" title="Taylor-Border-Slideshow-TX-16" data-description="West Texas Detention Facility, Sierra Blanca, Texas. "><img class="no-lazy flex-lazy" data-src="https://placesjournal.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Taylor-Border-Slideshow-TX-16.jpg" src="https://placesjournal.org/wp-content/themes/places/img/gallery-placeholder.jpg" alt="West Texas Detention Facility, Sierra Blanca, Texas." title="Click to Enlarge" /></a><p class="flex-caption"><span class="slideshow-label">Slideshow</span>West Texas Detention Facility, Sierra Blanca, Texas.</p></li><li><a class="gallery-zoom" href="https://placesjournal.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Taylor-Border-Slideshow-TX-17.jpg" title="Taylor-Border-Slideshow-TX-17" data-description="Webb County Detention Center, Laredo, Texas. "><img class="no-lazy flex-lazy" data-src="https://placesjournal.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Taylor-Border-Slideshow-TX-17.jpg" src="https://placesjournal.org/wp-content/themes/places/img/gallery-placeholder.jpg" alt="Webb County Detention Center, Laredo, Texas." title="Click to Enlarge" /></a><p class="flex-caption"><span class="slideshow-label">Slideshow</span>Webb County Detention Center, Laredo, Texas.</p></li><li><a class="gallery-zoom" href="https://placesjournal.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Taylor-Border-Slideshow-TX-18.jpg" title="Taylor-Border-Slideshow-TX-18" data-description="Rio Grande Detention Center, Laredo, Texas. "><img class="no-lazy flex-lazy" data-src="https://placesjournal.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Taylor-Border-Slideshow-TX-18.jpg" src="https://placesjournal.org/wp-content/themes/places/img/gallery-placeholder.jpg" alt="Rio Grande Detention Center, Laredo, Texas." title="Click to Enlarge" /></a><p class="flex-caption"><span class="slideshow-label">Slideshow</span>Rio Grande Detention Center, Laredo, Texas.</p></